column3: Why is this only happening on macos?

Because on Mac, the `AppTests::appTests()` gets skipped and misses the `ECC_Stop()` which would have cured the issue that `ECC_Start()` gets double initialized through `RPCNestedTests::rpcNestedTests()` -> `TestingSetup test`.\n\nI don't know if we could get rid of `TestingSetup test` in `RPCNestedTests::rpcNestedTests()` though.
